	Kana-Kanji Conversion Front-end alya

This front-end, "alya" is a sample implementation for evaluating the XIMP protocol.
It uses sj3 as a conversion engine in this release.

Install
	Please edit the Imakefile.

	SONYDIR
		Sony's contributed directory which contains sj3 library and
		headers.

	CCONVDIR
		cconv library's directory which included kinput (in X11R4).

Note
	This front-end supports only "over-the-spot" input style.
